@startuml
title Access Log Viewing

|Super Administrator|
start
:Open access log page;

|System|

  :Load access logs;
  :Display log records;

  |Super Administrator|
  :Enter filter or search criteria;

  |System|
  if (Filter applied?) then (Yes)
    :Retrieve filtered logs;
    :Display filtered results;
  else (No)
    :Display recent logs;
  endif

  if (CSV and /or PDF export requested?) then (Yes)
    :Generate CSV export;
    :Provide file download;
  else (No)
  endif

end
@enduml